f=Engineering/mia/custom/ui-accessibility-standards/assets/a11y-checklist.md · h1:Accessibility Checklist mia/ui-accessibility-standards=WCAG baseline. Verified real browser (frontend-verification), asserted. Component library tokens design-tokens. · h2:Components=Reused existing component before creating new one, New component added shared library, built design tokens (no hardcoded values) · h2:Semantic HTML=Correct elements (`<button>`, `<a>`, `<nav>`, `<label>`…) div+onclick, ARIA semantics genuinely fall short, substitute · k:board=interaction operable without mouse, Visible focus indicator; logical tab order; keyboard traps · h2:Screen reader=Meaningful labels; correct roles, Alt text informative images; empty alt decorative, Form fields associated labels · h2:Contrast sizing (WCAG AA)=Text meets contrast (token pairing failing pairing atlas finding), Touch targets adequately sized; text resizable · h2:States (accessible includes these)=Loading error empty states present (consuming raj's API contract) · h2:Verified=Checked real browser (Agentation quinn Reticle/Playwright) ref: ___